	   <tr><td colspan=2>I'd stick with a piercing weapon.<br>Try and get a giant snake fang cheap (1pp or so if you're not high level enough to kill the snakes that drop these), or a dragoon dirk for like 30pp if you have that kind of money. I forget the stats on the giant snake fang, but i know a dragoon dirk is about 6damage 22delay with +3 dexterity.<br><br>Most of the powerful stat enhancing weapons a wizard can wield are 1h blunt staves, but our mind allows us the advantage of not needing to use weapons to do the most damage. Around level 26 when you know you don't need to melee at all anymore you should look into getting a staff of the wheel, 10damage 100delay (horrid damage output), but +10 intelligence, +10mana, and +10hp. At level 50, 10 mana is equivalent to 1 point of intelligence. At level 1, 1 mana is equivalent to 1 point of intelligence.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
